WEBVTT

00:00.320 --> 00:03.566
As we step through the entrance, we're greeted by the modern architecture

00:03.670 --> 00:07.006
and inviting ambiance. The entrance sets the

00:07.030 --> 00:10.350
tone for what lies ahead, a world of exploration and

00:10.382 --> 00:11.314
discovery.

00:14.294 --> 00:18.310
The reception area welcomes us with warmth and efficiency.

00:18.502 --> 00:22.310
Here you'll find self check in and checkout facilities for books

00:22.422 --> 00:25.582
as well as a convenient bag counter for storing your belongings

00:25.638 --> 00:29.412
during your visit. Need a caffeine boost or

00:29.428 --> 00:32.972
a quick bite to eat? Look no further than Nescafe,

00:33.068 --> 00:36.740
conveniently located within the library premises. Whether you're craving

00:36.772 --> 00:40.060
a snack or a full meal, Nescafe offers a variety of

00:40.092 --> 00:43.676
dining options to fuel your mind and body. As we

00:43.700 --> 00:47.356
make our way through the library, we encounter lifts and stairs leading

00:47.380 --> 00:50.828
to different levels. Take a moment to relax and soak in

00:50.836 --> 00:53.544
the sunlight in the cozy sofa seating area.

00:54.824 --> 00:58.184
The open layout creates a welcoming atmosphere perfect

00:58.224 --> 01:01.564
for both solitary study sessions and group collaborations.

01:03.344 --> 01:07.328
For PhD scholars, dedicated study and conference rooms

01:07.376 --> 01:11.364
provide a conducive environment for research and scholarly pursuits.

01:11.704 --> 01:15.384
These spaces offer a blend of comfort and productivity.

01:15.544 --> 01:19.592
Equipped with desks, plug points, sofas, and bookshelves,

01:19.768 --> 01:23.376
the Shiv Nadar Institution of eminent Central Library is

01:23.400 --> 01:26.896
the soul of the institution and it has an extensive collection

01:26.920 --> 01:30.048
of books, scientific and technical journals,

01:30.176 --> 01:33.880
and electronic reference materials for satisfying the

01:33.912 --> 01:37.604
academic and research needs of students and faculty community.

01:38.184 --> 01:41.688
There is a reference section, circulation section,

01:41.856 --> 01:45.132
audio visual section, periodical section,

01:45.288 --> 01:47.504
book bank, and digital library.

01:48.084 --> 01:51.660
Let's ascend to the first floor. Here, we encounter a

01:51.692 --> 01:54.904
separate collection dedicated to scholarly research.

01:55.644 --> 01:59.764
In the SNU library, you'll find a treasure trove of academic

01:59.804 --> 02:03.644
literature and resources curated to support advanced

02:03.684 --> 02:07.564
studies and research endeavors. Step into our inviting

02:07.644 --> 02:11.356
library space and let yourself unwind. Amidst the cozy seating

02:11.420 --> 02:15.148
arrangements, thoughtfully designed individual cubicles,

02:15.236 --> 02:19.076
and tranquil study nooks. With shelves lined

02:19.100 --> 02:22.812
with an extensive array of books spanning various genres

02:22.868 --> 02:26.148
and subjects, you'll find yourself immersed in a sanctuary

02:26.236 --> 02:28.024
of knowledge and imagination.

02:29.204 --> 02:33.148
Whether you're embarking on a scholarly pursuit or seeking solace in

02:33.156 --> 02:35.384
the pages of a captivating novel,

02:36.004 --> 02:39.072
our library provides the perfect environment to study,

02:39.108 --> 02:42.164
stimulate your intellect, and soothe your soul.

02:42.984 --> 02:46.280
So take a moment to breathe, to explore, and to

02:46.312 --> 02:50.484
revel in the endless possibilities that await within these walls.

